==Ugaritic==

===Etymology===
From Proto-Semitic.

===Pronunciation===
Reconstructed as */lubuʔ-u/ (in nominative singular).

===Noun===
'''lbủ''', {{m}}, {{p}} ''lbủm'' (nominative)
# [[Lion]]: a large cat, ''Panthera leo'', native to Africa and formerly to much of Europe.
#:''pnpš npš lbỉm thw'', for my appetite is the appetite of the lions of the waste.

====Scientific names====
*''[[Panthera leo]]''

